Subject: Restore Global Settings Error
Description: Under device control, when we attempt reverting to global settings for specific computers, it works for some and does not work for others. For those it doesn't work for, it seems to inherit settings from another user, even though computer settings have priority. Server version is 5.9.4.0 but that did not show in your selection menu for the ticket.
Solution_Comment__c: Closing ticket as issue was resolved when custom user settings were reset to global for users that were showing in the two machines as getting its settings inherited from.
